{"data":[{"name":"88:1","price":"(നബിയേ,) ആ മൂടുന്ന സംഭവത്തെ(1) സംബന്ധിച്ച വര്‍ത്തമാനം നിനക്ക് വന്നുകിട്ടിയോ?","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡغَٰشِيَةِ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5968,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1) ഭയവും അമ്പരപ്പും എല്ലാവരെയും ആവരണം ചെയ്യുന്ന അന്ത്യദിനമത്രെ ഉദ്ദേശ്യം.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"hal atāka ḥadīthu al-ghāshiyati ","translations":["Has","(there) come to you","(the) news","(of) the Overwhelming","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["hal","atāka","ḥadīthu","al-ghāshiyati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1200],[3,1200,2050],[4,2050,3925]]}},{"name":"88:2","price":"അന്നേ ദിവസം ചില മുഖങ്ങള്‍ താഴ്മകാണിക്കുന്നതും","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ خَٰشِعَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5969,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wujūhun yawma-idhin khāshiʿatun ","translations":["Faces","that Day","(will be) humbled","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wujūhun","yawma-idhin","khāshiʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,3160],[3,3160,4965]]}},{"name":"88:3","price":"പണിയെടുത്ത് ക്ഷീണിച്ചതുമായിരിക്കും.(2)","arabic":"عَامِلَةٞ نَّاصِبَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5970,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2) അല്ലാഹുവിന്റെ വിചാരണയെയും ശിക്ഷയെയും പറ്റിയുള്ള ഭയം നിമിത്തം കീഴ്‌പ്പോട്ട് താഴ്ന്നവയായിരിക്കും ആ മുഖങ്ങള്‍. അവര്‍ ഭൗതിക ലക്ഷ്യങ്ങള്‍ക്കുവേണ്ടിയുള്ള പ്രയത്‌നങ്ങളോ തെറ്റായ മതാനുഷ്ഠാനങ്ങളോ ചെയ്ത് ക്ഷീണിച്ചവരായിരിക്കും. പക്ഷെ, അന്ത്യദിനത്തില്‍ അതൊന്നും അവര്‍ക്ക് ഉപകാരപ്പെടുകയില്ല.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿāmilatun nāṣibatun ","translations":["Laboring","exhausted","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿāmilatun","nāṣibatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1210],[2,1210,3985]]}},{"name":"88:4","price":"ചൂടേറിയ അഗ്നിയില്‍ അവ പ്രവേശിക്കുന്നതാണ്‌.","arabic":"تَصۡلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5971,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"taṣlā nāran ḥāmiyatan ","translations":["They will burn","(in) a Fire","intensely hot","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["taṣlā","nāran","ḥāmiyatan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1630],[3,1630,3355]]}},{"name":"88:5","price":"ചുട്ടുതിളക്കുന്ന ഒരു ഉറവില്‍ നിന്ന് അവര്‍ക്കു കുടിപ്പിക്കപ്പെടുന്നതാണ്‌.","arabic":"تُسۡقَىٰ مِنۡ عَيۡنٍ ءَانِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5972,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"tus'qā min ʿaynin āniyatin ","translations":["They will be given to drink","from","a spring","boiling","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["tus'qā","min","ʿaynin","āniyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,1090],[3,1090,2070],[4,2070,3715]]}},{"name":"88:6","price":"ദരീഇല്‍(3) നിന്നല്ലാതെ അവര്‍ക്ക് യാതൊരു ആഹാരവുമില്ല.","arabic":"لَّيۡسَ لَهُمۡ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5973,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3) വളരെ കയ്പ്പുള്ള ഒരു ചെടിയാണ് 'ദ്വരീഅ്' എന്നാണ് പല വ്യാഖ്യാതാക്കളും അഭിപ്രായപ്പെട്ടിട്ടുള്ളത്.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"laysa lahum ṭaʿāmun illā min ḍarīʿin ","translations":["Not is","for them","food","except","from","a bitter thorny plant","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["laysa","lahum","ṭaʿāmun","illā","min","ḍarīʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1200],[3,1200,2250],[4,2250,3180],[5,3180,4510],[6,4510,7285]]}},{"name":"88:7","price":"അത് പോഷണം നല്‍കുകയില്ല. വിശപ്പിന് ശമനമുണ്ടാക്കുകയുമില്ല.","arabic":"لَّا يُسۡمِنُ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِن جُوعٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5974,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"lā yus'minu walā yugh'nī min jūʿin ","translations":["Not","it nourishes","and not","it avails","from","hunger","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","yus'minu","walā","yugh'nī","min","jūʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,440],[2,440,1330],[3,1330,1860],[4,1860,2750],[5,2750,3090],[6,3090,6355]]}},{"name":"88:8","price":"ചില മുഖങ്ങള്‍ അന്നു തുടുത്തു മിനുത്തതായിരിക്കും.","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاعِمَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5975,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wujūhun yawma-idhin nāʿimatun ","translations":["Faces","that Day","(will be) joyful","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wujūhun","yawma-idhin","nāʿimatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,2430],[3,2430,5635]]}},{"name":"88:9","price":"അവയുടെ പ്രയത്നത്തെപ്പറ്റി തൃപ്തിയടഞ്ഞവയുമായിരിക്കും.(9)","arabic":"لِّسَعۡيِهَا رَاضِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5976,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"4) ഇഹലോകത്ത് തങ്ങള്‍ ചെയ്ത കര്‍മങ്ങള്‍ സഫലമായിത്തീര്‍ന്നതില്‍ അവര്‍ സംതൃപ്തരായിരിക്കും.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"lisaʿyihā rāḍiyatun ","translations":["With their effort","satisfied","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["lisaʿyihā","rāḍiyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,2965]]}},{"name":"88:10","price":"ഉന്നതമായ സ്വര്‍ഗത്തില്‍.","arabic":"فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5977,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fī jannatin ʿāliyatin ","translations":["In","a garden","elevated","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","jannatin","ʿāliyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2200],[3,2200,3725]]}},{"name":"88:11","price":"അവിടെ യാതൊരു നിരര്‍ത്ഥകമായ വാക്കും അവര്‍ കേള്‍ക്കുകയില്ല.","arabic":"لَّا تَسۡمَعُ فِيهَا لَٰغِيَةٗ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5978,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"lā tasmaʿu fīhā lāghiyatan ","translations":["Not","they will hear","therein","vain talk","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","tasmaʿu","fīhā","lāghiyatan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,1330],[3,1330,2280],[4,2280,3975]]}},{"name":"88:12","price":"അതില്‍ ഒഴുകിക്കൊണ്ടിരിക്കുന്ന അരുവിയുണ്ട്‌.","arabic":"فِيهَا عَيۡنٞ جَارِيَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5979,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhā ʿaynun jāriyatun ","translations":["Therein","(will be) a spring","flowing","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhā","ʿaynun","jāriyatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,810],[2,810,2400],[3,2400,4174]]}},{"name":"88:13","price":"അതില്‍ ഉയര്‍ത്തിവെക്കപ്പെട്ട കട്ടിലുകളും,","arabic":"فِيهَا سُرُرٞ مَّرۡفُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5980,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fīhā sururun marfūʿatun ","translations":["Therein","(will be) thrones","raised high","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fīhā","sururun","marfūʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1540],[3,1540,4315]]}},{"name":"88:14","price":"തയ്യാറാക്കി വെക്കപ്പെട്ട കോപ്പകളും,","arabic":"وَأَكۡوَابٞ مَّوۡضُوعَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5981,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-akwābun mawḍūʿatun ","translations":["And cups","put in place","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-akwābun","mawḍūʿatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,4005]]}},{"name":"88:15","price":"അണിയായി വെക്കപ്പെട്ട തലയണകളും,","arabic":"وَنَمَارِقُ مَصۡفُوفَةٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5982,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wanamāriqu maṣfūfatun ","translations":["And cushions","lined up","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["wanamāriqu","maṣfūfatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,3005]]}},{"name":"88:16","price":"വിരിച്ചുവെക്കപ്പെട്ട പരവതാനികളുമുണ്ട്‌.","arabic":"وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبۡثُوثَةٌ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5983,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wazarābiyyu mabthūthatun ","translations":["And carpets","spread out","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["wazarābiyyu","mabthūthatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1530],[2,1530,3475]]}},{"name":"88:17","price":"ഒട്ടകത്തിന്‍റെ നേര്‍ക്ക് അവര്‍ നോക്കുന്നില്ലേ?(5) അത് എങ്ങനെ സൃഷ്ടിക്കപ്പെട്ടിരിക്കുന്നു എന്ന്‌.","arabic":"أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡإِبِلِ كَيۡفَ خُلِقَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5984,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"5) മരുഭൂമിയിലെ മനുഷ്യന്റെ ആവശ്യങ്ങള്‍ നിറവേറ്റുന്ന, മരുഭൂമിയുടെ പ്രകൃതിയുമായി ഇണങ്ങിച്ചേരുന്ന ഒട്ടകത്തിന്റെ ശരീരഘടന വിസ്മയകരമാണ്. ഒട്ടകത്തെ സൂക്ഷ്മമായി നിരീക്ഷിക്കുന്ന ഏതൊരാള്‍ക്കും സൃഷ്ടികര്‍ത്താവിന്റെ സംവിധാനവൈഭവത്തെപ്പറ്റി ചിന്തിക്കാതിരിക്കാന്‍ കഴിയില്ല.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"afalā yanẓurūna ilā al-ibili kayfa khuliqat ","translations":["Then do not","they look","towards","the camels","how","they are created","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["afalā","yanẓurūna","ilā","al-ibili","kayfa","khuliqat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,2740],[3,2740,3130],[4,3130,4050],[5,4050,4670],[6,4670,5995]]}},{"name":"88:18","price":"ആകാശത്തേക്ക് (അവര്‍ നോക്കുന്നില്ലേ?) അത് എങ്ങനെ ഉയര്‍ത്തപ്പെട്ടിരിക്കുന്നു എന്ന്‌.","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5985,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ilā al-samāi kayfa rufiʿat ","translations":["And towards","the sky","how","it is raised","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ilā","al-samāi","kayfa","rufiʿat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,3240],[3,3240,3810],[4,3810,5175]]}},{"name":"88:19","price":"പര്‍വ്വതങ്ങളിലേക്ക് (അവര്‍ നോക്കുന്നില്ലേ?) അവ എങ്ങനെ നാട്ടിനിര്‍ത്തപ്പെട്ടിരിക്കുന്നുവെന്ന്‌.","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5986,"juzNumber":30,"footno